						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/the-prodigal-converses-with-the-land-a-poem-by-kwame-dawes/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">"The Prodigal Converses with the Land," a Poem by Kwame Dawes</h7>
			</a>
			The Prodigal Converses with the Land

I

Cape Coast:

I am a city in translation. What I say to you is not in the language
I...			
